# Deployment: Always Git, Not Local

- **Push to Git** – Deploy changes by committing and pushing to the connected Git repository. Vercel will pick up the push and deploy.
- **Do NOT run locally** – Do not run `npm run dev`, `pnpm dev`, or other local dev commands.
- **Exception** – Only run or test locally when the user explicitly says "deploy to local" or asks for local testing.
